          smoothly. Outside the world of coding, I find joy in chilling with friends and immersing myself in the
          timeless tunes of rock music, with Pink Floyd being a personal favorite. The call of the outdoors beckons me,
          and I often find myself on vacations, exploring picturesque destinations, with Kerala holding a special place
